title: Champion of Hermes
name: Spinymph - Champion of Hermes
printed_effect: When you Normal Cast this Spinymph you can Search your deck for a Hermes and add it to your hand. You can Disenchant {wind} from this Spinymph in order to Special Ascend it to Spinosect from your hand or deck.
